column5: at 4:46 it gets even better.  Throw it on fullscreen and enjoy.
Wow!  That is great.  Way better than most of the stuff on Youtube.  Or even most tv shows. Thanks for posting this.
Here's a good trailer for a muskie video.    A lot of it was shot on Lac Seul.  The very start of the video, where they're launching a boat, is at the lodge where I guide for.
For you guys that love flyfishing, check out Catch magazine..  It's an online magazine and completely free.  The pics they take are unbelievable.
